    <CompAttribute name="allTIBookingRefs" id="da267eac-3fef-4962-a31e-d03b37763814">
        <type name="StringArray"/>
        <text>Elements of this StringArray will store a Tracked Item ID and its Booking Ref code as:

	&lt;ID&gt;=&lt;Bookinf Ref&gt;

The "doStoreTIBookingRef" method can be used to store this pair, and the "getTIBookingRef"
method can be used to retrieve the Booking Ref for a Tracked Item.</text>
    </CompAttribute>
